  "Title": "#易错点#ssm伪静态方案：struts2 + urlRewrite",
  "Text": "<p>web.xml中的struts2 filter-mapping相应要添加request 和 forward：</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;</span></p><p><span>&lt;web-app version=\"2.4\" xmlns=\"http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/j2ee\"</span></p><p>xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"</p><p>xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/j2ee </p><p>http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/j2ee/web-app_2_4.xsd\"</p><p>id=\"WebApp_ID\"&gt;</p><p>&lt;display-name&gt;VPSWeb&lt;/display-name&gt;</p><p><span><br></span></p><p>&lt;context-param&gt;</p><p>&lt;param-name&gt;contextConfigLocation&lt;/param-name&gt;</p><p>&lt;param-value&gt;/WEB-INF/classes/applicationContext.xml&lt;/param-value&gt;</p><p>&lt;/context-param&gt;</p><p><span><br></span></p><p>&lt;listener&gt;</p><p>&lt;listener-class&gt;org.springframework.web.context.ContextLoaderListener&lt;/listener-class&gt;</p><p>&lt;/listener&gt;</p><p>&lt;!-- Set URL Rewrite Filter --&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-name&gt;UrlRewriteFilter&lt;/filter-name&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-class&gt;org.tuckey.web.filters.urlrewrite.UrlRewriteFilter&lt;/filter-class&gt;</p><p>&lt;/filter&gt;</p><p><span><br></span></p><p>&lt;filter-mapping&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-name&gt;UrlRewriteFilter&lt;/filter-name&gt;</p><p>&lt;url-pattern&gt;/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</p><p>&lt;dispatcher&gt;REQUEST&lt;/dispatcher&gt;</p><p>&lt;dispatcher&gt;FORWARD&lt;/dispatcher&gt;</p><p>&lt;/filter-mapping&gt;</p><p><span><br></span></p><p>&lt;filter&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-name&gt;struts2&lt;/filter-name&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-class&gt;</p><p>org.apache.struts2.dispatcher.ng.filter.StrutsPrepareAndExecuteFilter</p><p>&lt;/filter-class&gt;</p><p>&lt;/filter&gt;</p><p><span><br></span></p><p>&lt;filter-mapping&gt;</p><p>&lt;filter-name&gt;struts2&lt;/filter-name&gt;</p><p>&lt;url-pattern&gt;/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</p><p><span class=\"edui-filter-underline\">&lt;dispatcher&gt;REQUEST&lt;/dispatcher&gt;</span></p><p><span class=\"edui-filter-underline\">&lt;dispatcher&gt;FORWARD&lt;/dispatcher&gt;</span></p><p>&lt;/filter-mapping&gt;</p><p><span>&lt;/web-app&gt;</span></p>"
}
