  "Title": "[xPath] C# Xpath 解析HTML入门，使用方法教程",
  "Text": "<p>首先我们应该去下载一下Dll<br>目前的版本应该是HtmlAgilityPack.1.4.6的，<br>这里提供下载：<br><img id=\"8C8B63277B5FC288CEDE759C621286ED\"><span><a href=\"http://www.sufeinet.com/forum.php?mod=attachment&amp;aid=NTY1fDRiNTc2MTJlfDEzNzQ1MDYyOTB8MHwxOTQz\" target=\"_blank\">HtmlAgilityPack.1.4.6.rar</a><em>(835.11 KB, 下载次数: 198)</em></span><br>资源如下<br></p><p><img id=\"794C5657D6A699861F285D027C8E2699\"></p><br>大家选择一下自己的版本就行了<br>然后把Dll引用到你的项目中来<br>使用代码如下<br><p></p><p></p><p>普通浏览复制代码</p><p></p><ol><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> HttpHelper http = <span>new</span> HttpHelper<span>(</span><span>)</span><span>;</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HttpItem item = <span>new</span> HttpItem<span>(</span><span>)</span> { URL = <span>\"http://www.cckan.net\"</span> }<span>;</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HtmlDocument html = <span>new</span> HtmlDocument<span>(</span><span>)</span><span>;</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;html.LoadHtml<span>(</span>http.GetHtml<span>(</span>item<span>)</span><span>)</span><span>;</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HtmlAgilityPack.HtmlNode htmlNode = html.DocumentNode<span>;</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>//要取出的Xpath标签</span></p></li><li><p><img id=\"FB4C847BC4E3E8F74946B9D57EF7D5F0\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HtmlAgilityPack.HtmlNode div = htmlNode.SelectSingleNode<span>(</span><span>\".//*[@id='nv_forum']/div[6]/div[1]/a[1]\"</span><span>)</span><span>;</span></p></li></ol><p></p><p></p><p></p><br>大家会问了那个这Xpath代码怎么取得呢，其实这个更简单<br>大家打开火狐浏览器，安装好FirBug，具体的安装方法大家网上看一下吧，<br><p><img id=\"329D4A3FE28E007F098075BB3762898A\"></p><br>单击一下然后去选择你要获取的内容<br><p><img id=\"AB773970E6F2EC098FC0CBA8513FBAA9\"></p><br>然后右键<br><p><img id=\"29DECFBF84C994829CAAC6B6318DABB5\"></p><br>这样就得到了<br>"
}
