  "Title": "WPF.01.-使用console编译C#",
  "Text": "<p><span>1.安装完visual studio之后，会有一个控制台，这里可以手动编译程序</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>2.打开控制台，写好程序。例如附件1的app.txt内容</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>3.控制台cd到当前app.txt目录</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>4.csc app.txt</span></p><p><span>会说找不到命名空间MessageBox</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>5.需要引入类库 C:\\Program Files\\Reference Assemblies\\Microsoft\\Framework\\.NETFramework\\v4.0\\Profile\\Client\\PresentationFramework.dll</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>6.csc /r:\"C:\\Program Files\\Reference Assemblies\\Microsoft\\Framework\\.NETFramework\\v4.0\\Profile\\Client\\PresentationFramework.dll\" /t:exe app.txt</span></p><p><span>控制台应用程序</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>7.不想出现控制台</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>csc /r:\"C:\\Program Files\\Reference Assemblies\\Microsoft\\Framework\\.NETFramework\\v4.0\\Profile\\Client\\PresentationFramework.dll\" /t:winexe app.txt</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>8.编译成库</span></p><p><span><br></span></p><p><span>csc /r:\"C:\\Program Files\\Reference Assemblies\\Microsoft\\Framework\\.NETFramework\\v4.0\\Profile\\Client\\PresentationFramework.dll\" /t:library app.txt</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>附件1(app.txt)：</p><pre config=\"brush:c#;toolbar:false;\">namespace MyApp\n{\n    class Program\n    {\n        static void Main(string[] args)\n        {\n            System.Windows.MessageBox.Show(\"Hello 张微\");\n        }\n    }\n}</pre><p>&nbsp;</p>"
}
