  "Text": "<p>1.配置共享无线网</p><pre config=\"brush:ps;toolbar:false;\">netsh wlan set hostednetwork mode=allow ssid=YourNetWorkName key=YourPassword</pre><p>2.开启无线网共享<br></p><pre config=\"brush:ps;toolbar:false;\">netsh wlan start hostednetwork</pre><p>3.关闭无线网共享<br></p><pre config=\"brush:ps;toolbar:false;\">netsh wlan stop hostednetwork</pre><p>附件：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/share/link?shareid=499634&amp;uk=3306034113\" title=\"windows7无线网络共享设置.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">windows7无线网络共享设置.pdf</a></p>"
