;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://chinaitlab.com/\" target=\"_blank\">中国IT实验室</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.chinaunix.net/\" target=\"_blank\">ChinaUnix</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.bluesnews.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Blue's News</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.51cto.com/\" target=\"_blank\">51CTO</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.iteye.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ITEYE</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.infoq.com/\" target=\"_blank\">InfoQ</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://news.ycombinator.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hacker News</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.churchtecharts.org/\" target=\"_blank\">CHURCH TECH ARTS</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.reddit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">reddit</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.linuxvirtualserver.org/HighAvailability.html\" target=\"_blank\">linuxvirtualserver</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.linuxpilot.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Linux Pilot</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.codinghorror.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">Coding Horror</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/\" target=\"_blank\">stackoverflow</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://highscalability.com/\" target=\"_blank\">highscalability</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><br></p><h2>无谓分类的：</h2><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>刘未鹏 </strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://mindhacks.cn/\">http://mindhacks.cn/</a> &nbsp;<br>绝对的绝对的大牛，在大一时读到他的<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://mindhacks.cn/2009/05/17/seven-years-in-nju/\">《我在南大的七年》</a>，从此成了我和我身边很多朋友的必读博客。由C++转型写思维和学习认知的博文，并在豆瓣推荐了一些列<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/people/pongba/doulists\">经典书单</a>。11年博客整理出版<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/6709809/\">《暗时间》</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>Matrix67</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.matrix67.com/blog/\">http://www.matrix67.com/blog/</a><br>喜欢平面几何, 组合数学, 图论…博客里都是些很有意思的数学题目，听说现在的HR都要读他的blog。12年整理出版了<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/10779597/\">《思考的乐趣》</a>。然后的然后，他是北大中文系的学生。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>徐宥</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.youxu.info/\">http://blog.youxu.info/</a><br>Google软件工程师，我从<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/4006425/\">《我是一只IT小小鸟》</a>中读到《<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.youxu.info/2009/08/06/my-undergraduate-year/\">我的大学</a>》开始关注他的博客，也是个涉猎广泛，喜欢思考的大牛。每个有志奋斗于程序之路的同学都应当读一读前辈的“<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.youxu.info/21-days/\">十年学会程序设计</a>”。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>赵劼</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.zhaojie.me/\">http://blog.zhaojie.me/</a><br>IBM高级咨询师，InfoQ中文站编辑，关注微软技术。推荐系列：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.zhaojie.me/2009/12/valuable-posts-index.html#prog-lang-trend\">编程语言的发展趋势及未来方向</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>July</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/v_JULY_v\">http://blog.csdn.net/v_JULY_v</a><br>狂热算法，热爱数据挖掘，学学NLP&amp;机器学习，折腾视频编/解码。著有访问量颇高的《<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/column/details/ms100.html\">微软面试100题系列</a>》，在csdn的小活动“<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/blogdevteam/article/details/7838383\">我最喜欢的技术博客</a>”中被推荐了N多次……</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>白明</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://tonybai.com/\">http://tonybai.com/</a><br>Neusoft某开发部技术总监，资深C程序员，对Common Lisp、Python等小众语言也有涉猎，热爱开源，<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/10555435/\">《七周七语言》</a>译者。<br></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>懒人有禅</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.lanrenux.com/\">http://www.lanrenux.com/</a><br>一群清北大牛建立的集体博客，关注用户体验。我从<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://jiepang.com/\">街旁</a>创始人<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.yangyc.com/\">杨远骋</a>的About Me里看到的，尤其看<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.lanrenux.com/?page_id=13\">“懒人一览”</a>时深刻体会到了所谓的“物以类聚”。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>图灵社区 </strong><a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.ituring.com.cn/\">http://www.ituring.com.cn/</a><br>有图灵的新书，作者访谈之列，还有系列图书推荐。</p><br class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><br></p><h2>偏重CV的：</h2><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>邹宇华</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://yuhuazou.sinaapp.com/\">http://yuhuazou.sinaapp.com/</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\">北京航博士生,关注机器视觉与多机器人协同。分享推荐了不少科研资源：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://yuhuazou.sinaapp.com/%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90/\">资源</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>JerryLead</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/jerrylead/\">http://www.cnblogs.com/jerrylead/</a><br>他写的机器学习：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/jerrylead/tag/Machine%20Learning/\">Machine Learning</a>系列很认真，非常非常有价值。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>张驰原</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.pluskid.org/\">http://blog.pluskid.org/</a><br>NJU的，关注机器学习、模式识别、信息检索等。搜到过他的<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.pluskid.org/?page_id=683\">支持向量机系列</a>，理解的很通透。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>yang_xian521</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/yang_xian521\">http://blog.csdn.net/yang_xian521</a><br>OpenCV大牛，很棒的《<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/column/details/opencv-manual.html\">OpenCV学习笔记</a>》专栏。我记得2.4刚没多久，前辈就更新博客了。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>Sophia_qing</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/abcjennifer\">http://blog.csdn.net/abcjennifer</a><br>浙江大学CS硕士在读，关注计算机视觉，机器学习，算法等。看过他写的<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/abcjennifer/article/details/8002329\">ML学习笔记</a>，挺有特点的。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><br></p><h2>IT评论或杂文的：</h2><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>酷壳</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://coolshell.cn/\">http://coolshell.cn/</a><br>陈皓，Amazon中国任研发经理，热衷于分享技术见闻，知识，趋势。<br></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>IT外刊评论网 </strong><a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.aqee.net/\">http://www.aqee.net/</a><br>文章都是翻译的外国IT方面的评论、访谈，偏重于软件方面，涵盖Java、.NET、Ruby、SOA、敏捷和架构等。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>月光博客</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.williamlong.info/\">http://www.williamlong.info/</a><br>龙威廉，关注电脑技术、网站架设互联网、搜索引擎行业、Web 2.0等。<br></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><br></p><h2>科普，心理，杂七杂八的：</h2><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>科学松鼠会</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://songshuhui.net/\">http://songshuhui.net/</a><br>几乎所有有订阅习惯的朋友都会订阅的科普博客，“剥开科学的坚果，帮助人们领略科学之美妙”。经常在中科院进行科普讲座，关注豆瓣小站<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://site.douban.com/songshuhui/\">科学松鼠会</a>就会受到他们同城活动的邀请。</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>褪墨</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.mifengtd.cn/\">http://www.mifengtd.cn/</a><br>关注时间管理，个人提升和演讲技巧。把事情做到更好。有可下载的推荐文集：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.mifengtd.cn/articles/mifengtd-best-articles-download-national-day-gifts.html\">《褪墨优秀文章选摘》</a><br></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>PSY BLOG</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.spring.org.uk/\">http://www.spring.org.uk/</a> <br>林肯大学Phd <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.spring.org.uk/about-this-blog\">Jeremy Dean</a>的心理学小站，关注思维模式，认知神经科学等，内容比较前沿，推荐<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.spring.org.uk/2007/11/10-piercing-insights-into-human-nature.php\">《Why We do Dumb or Irrational Things:10 Brilliant Social Psychology Studies》</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>世纪心理沙龙</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.xlxcn.net/\">http://www.xlxcn.net/</a><br>很不错的一个心理学小站，推荐站长<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.xlxcn.net/about\">迟毓凯</a>推荐的<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.xlxcn.net/archives/1902\">《走进心理学》</a></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>李笑来</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://lixiaolai.com/\">http://lixiaolai.com/</a><br>原新东方老师，现笑来教育信息咨询有限公司合伙人。<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/3609132/\">《把时间当做朋友》</a>作者，文章都比较简单，但很有启发。<br></p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><strong>伯乐在线</strong> <a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.jobbole.com/category/programmer/\">http://blog.jobbole.com/category/programmer/</a><br>分先原创、译文。</p><h2>附录</h2><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\">声明：我不保证附录的链接都能正常访问……</p><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\"><br></p><h3>附录1：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://book.douban.com/subject/4006425/\">《我是一只IT小小鸟》</a>里的小小鸟们：</h3><p class=\"edui-filter-align-left\">蒋宇东 现就职于上海某公司（C++程序员）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/NewNebuladream\">http://blog.csdn.net/NewNebuladream</a><br>居振梁 博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://wargrey.yo2.cn/\">http://wargrey.yo2.cn</a><br>刘帅 现就职于Amazon（SDE-Test）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://lsthu.spaces.live.com/\">http://lsthu.spaces.live.com/</a><br>李成 现就职于北京飞维美地信息技术有限公司（软件工程师）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://www.perlfect.org/\">http://www.perlfect.org</a><br>温卫斌 现就职于中国农业银行软件开发中心 博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://terry-pekingssm.spaces.live.com/\">http://terry-pekingssm.spaces.live.com</a><br>胡江堂 现就职于赛诺菲巴斯德（SAS程序员）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://li-and-jiang.com/blog/\">http://li-and-jiang.com/blog/</a><br>辜新星 现就职于Google（助理产品经理）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://guxinxing.blogbus.com/\">http://guxinxing.blogbus.com/</a><br>刘未鹏 现就职于微软亚洲研究院（程序员）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://mindhacks.cn/\">http://mindhacks.cn</a><br>唐雅薇 现就职于IBM中国研发中心（上海）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://cubbyvivi.blogbus.com/\">http://cubbyvivi.blogbus.com/</a><br>张弦 现就职于百度（软件工程师）博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://stonefish9.blogbus.com/\">http://stonefish9.blogbus.com/</a><br>秦琴 现就职于中国银行 博客：<a class=\"edui-filter-decoration-none\" href=\"http://clalietsin.spaces.live.com/\">http://clalietsin.spaces.live.com/</a><br>