  "Text": "<pre config=\"white-space:pre-wrap;word-wrap:break-word;color:#362e2b;padding:0px;border:0px;outline:0px;font-size:11.818181991577148px;vertical-align:baseline;background-color:#faffff;font-family:'ヒラギノ角ゴ pro w3', 'hiragino kaku gothic pro', メイリオ, meiryo, 'ｍｓ ｐゴシック', sans-serif;line-height:1.5;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">0. git fetch\n0.1 git checkout master\n0.2 git pull orgin master//Get the new code from remote:master\n1. Create new branch by Xcode (local).\n2. work\n3. commit\n4. rebase（Do it before commit if necessary）\n5. git push orign BRANCHE_NAME (It is Ok by Xcode)\n6. pull request</pre>"
