  "Text": "<p>早几天那晚临睡前,一直在折腾vpn的事,毕竟总用91vpn也是需要money的,每月一二十的费用不少啊!按照一些教程做起来倒是容易,但是结果却是给我800错误,找了些资料,都没什么结果,所以干脆直接找\"一键安装\"包!下面这是还是挺有用的.一试就成了!<br>因为不想把文档上传到服务器上,下面把文档内容copy下来,你复制保存下来就行了.使用方法下面也有.<br>[#是空行，你可以删除]<br><strong>一键安装包</strong><br><code><br>yum remove -y pptpd ppp<br>iptables --flush POSTROUTING --table nat<br>iptables --flush FORWARD<br>rm -rf /etc/pptpd.conf<br>rm -rf /etc/ppp<br>#<br>wget http://www.diahosting.com/dload/dkms-2.0.17.5-1.noarch.rpm<br>wget http://www.diahosting.com/dload/kernel_ppp_mppe-1.0.2-3dkms.noarch.rpm<br>wget http://www.diahosting.com/dload/pptpd-1.3.4-1.rhel5.1.i386.rpm<br>wget http://www.diahosting.com/dload/ppp-2.4.4-9.0.rhel5.i386.rpm<br>#<br>yum -y install make libpcap iptables gcc-c++ logrotate tar cpio perl pam tcp_wrappers<br>rpm -ivh dkms-2.0.17.5-1.noarch.rpm<br>rpm -ivh kernel_ppp_mppe-1.0.2-3dkms.noarch.rpm<br>rpm -qa kernel_ppp_mppe<br>rpm -Uvh ppp-2.4.4-9.0.rhel5.i386.rpm<br>rpm -ivh pptpd-1.3.4-1.rhel5.1.i386.rpm<br>#<br>mknod /dev/ppp c 108 0<br>echo 1 &gt; /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward<br>echo \"mknod /dev/ppp c 108 0\" &gt;&gt; /etc/rc.local<br>echo \"echo 1 &gt; /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward\" &gt;&gt; /etc/rc.local<br>echo \"localip 172.16.36.1\" &gt;&gt; /etc/pptpd.conf<br>echo \"remoteip 172.16.36.2-254\" &gt;&gt; /etc/pptpd.conf<br>echo \"ms-dns 8.8.8.8\" &gt;&gt; /etc/ppp/options.pptpd<br>echo \"ms-dns 8.8.4.4\" &gt;&gt; /etc/ppp/options.pptpd<br>#<br>pass=`openssl rand 6 -base64`<br>if [ \"$1\" != \"\" ]<br>then pass=$1<br>fi<br>#<br>echo \"vpn pptpd ${pass} *\" &gt;&gt; /etc/ppp/chap-secrets<br>#<br>iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 172.16.36.0/24 -j SNAT --to-source `ifconfig | grep 'inet addr:'| grep -v '127.0.0.1' | cut -d: -f2 | awk 'NR==1 { print $1}'`<br>iptables -A FORWARD -p tcp --syn -s 172.16.36.0/24 -j TCPMSS --set-mss 1356<br>service iptables save<br>#<br>chkconfig iptables on<br>chkconfig pptpd on<br>#<br>service iptables start<br>service pptpd start<br>#<br>echo \"VPN service is installed, your VPN username is vpn, VPN password is ${pass}\"<br>#<br></code><br><strong>使用方法</strong>：<br>登陆vps之后直接<br>上传此文档［或者你不想上传，直接用此命令下载 wget http://www.diahosting.com/dload/pptpd.sh］<br>运行　sh pptpd.sh<br>安装完成后会提示vpn用户名和密码。<br><strong>VPN用户管理</strong><br>直接编辑/etc/ppp/chap-secrets文件，按照相同格式添加用户名和密码即可。<br>[caption id=\"attachment_337\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"469\"]</p><p>vpn连接图</p>"
