  "Text": "<p>1. Each click can have to how much money do depends on the number of such adwords ads, you and Google to share the revenue. (do those on the advertising many industry can earn more money.<br>2. Adsense income may be high to make you incredible, than other forms of advertising to make money, the key is your web site to clean, professional, flow, and advertising to obvious, or closely and website content fuses in together.<br>3. Get high income, it is critical to have a lot of page display number and high CTR.<br>4. to design the web, might as well considering the Adsense ads position! Such as 728 * 90 ads a, 336 * 280 ads a placement put where good? When the design can think, set aside a good position put advertising is a high income of a very important condition.<br>5. To increase your click-throughs, design a simple, uncluttered page is key! Page comfortable, advertising is very natural, very significant, click rate natural high!<br>6. Adsense ads should seize the first eye.<br>7. Border and web page background the same color can get good effect (is no border), can have a try, really good!<br>8. The content of a page only around a theme, which helps to gogole provide and related to the themes in advertising.<br>9. Less and Google offsetting links, help the customer point your advertising links.<br>10. If there is a destination to do a certain keywords, web page name to use the keywords, title, keywords, and a content appropriate to use some of the key words. This and do SEO is a bit similar!<br>10. If the ads that appear to pass on your page link text, can change another try.<br> <br>11. Try bottom also put a advertisement, visitors to pull to the bottom might point it? !<br>12. Don't old acquisition others things, or computer automatically generated dongdong, make some original dongdong, visitors like, Google also like.<br>13. Think of a way to (if use channels or click on the statistical tools) to study your income, this and SEO research flow is similar.<br>1.每次点击能得多少钱决定于做此类adwords广告的人数，你和google一起分享这笔收入。（做那些投放广告多的行业可以赚到更多的钱。）<br>2.Adsense收入可以高到令你难以置信，比其它广告形式赚的钱都多，关键是你的网站要干净，专业，有流量，并且广告要明显，或是紧密地和网站内容融合在一起。<br>3.获得高收入的关键是有很大的页面展示数和很高的点击率。<br>4.重新设计网页时，不妨考虑到Adsense的广告位！如728*90广告位，336*280的广告位的放置放哪里好呢？设计时可以想想，留出一个好位置放广告是获得高收入的一个很重要的条件。<br>5.要获得高点击率，设计一个简洁，整齐的网页很关键！页面舒服些，广告很自然，很显著，点击率自然高喽！<br>6.Adsense广告要抓住第一眼球。<br>7.边框和网页背景同色可以获得不错的效果（就是没有边框），可以试试，真的不错的！<br>8.一个页面的内容只围绕一个主题，这有助于gogole提供和主题相关的广告。<br>9.少一些和google相抵的链接，有助于用户点你的广告链接。<br>10.如果是有目的地做某一个关键词，网页名要用这个关键词，title,keywords,及第一段内容适当用些这个关键词。这和做ＳＥＯ有点类似喽！<br>10.如果发现出现的广告不是要关，可以试试网页上的链接文字，可以改成别的试试看。<br>11.试试底部也放个广告，访问者拉到底部说不定会点它一下呢？！<br>12.别老采集别人的东东，或者是电脑自动生成的东东，搞点原创东东，访问者喜欢，google也喜欢。<br>13.想办法（如用渠道或是点击统计工具）来研究你的收入，这和ＳＥＯ研究流量是类似的。<br></p>"
